---
export const prerender = true;

import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy"
  description="What we collect, what we don't, and what happens with your email."
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive">Privacy</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 font-serif text-4xl text-ink sm:text-5xl">
      What we collect, what we don't.
    </h1>

    <div class="prose-lt mt-10 space-y-6 text-ink/90">
      <p>
        We try to collect as little as possible. Here's the honest list of
        what shows up in our records and why it's there.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-ink">Email signups</h2>
      <p>
        If you give us your email address through the subscribe form, we add
        it to our newsletter list so we can send you the Saturday email. We
        derive a first name from the part of your email before the @ to make
        the messages a little less robotic. That's it. We don't sell, rent,
        or share the list. You can unsubscribe at the bottom of any email
        and we'll take you off immediately.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-ink">Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        We use Google Analytics 4 and the Meta Pixel to understand which
        guides people read, which links get clicked, and which ads are worth
        running. These tools set cookies and log standard things like the
        page you visited, your approximate location, and your device type.
        They do not log anything about who you are personally.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-ink">Affiliate links</h2>
      <p>
        When you click a "shop this" link, your browser is redirected to a
        retailer (usually Amazon) with a tag that tells them the visit came
        from us. The retailer's own privacy policy then governs what they
        do with your visit and purchase. We don't see what you bought, only
        that you clicked.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-ink">Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        The cookies on this site are set by the analytics tools above and by
        Cloudflare, which handles our DNS. We don't set any of our own
        tracking cookies.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-ink">Questions</h2>
      <p>
        If you'd like a copy of what we have on file for you, or you'd like
        us to delete it, write to us and we'll take care of it within a few
        days.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose-lt p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .prose-lt h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
</style>
